TRUGG v1.0 A superb DOS arcade puzzle game
featuring stunning fully-rendered 3D
graphics throughout, extensive in-game
animation and a heart pumping soundtrack.
Guide Trugg through 20 cavernous
conundrums collecting treasures while
avoiding boulders, guns, forcefields and
guardians. Registered version includes
WYSIWYG level editor. Requires 386 or
above VGA, 560kb, Soundblaster or
compatible optional
